        "Sakai Moving Service (9039) — operator of the Sakai Hikkoshi Center brand — is Japan's largest household-moving company, the familiar 'panda' moving brand seen across the country. Its core business is residential and office relocations: packing, hauling and unpacking customers' belongings when they move. Around that it has added related logistics and distribution services. It is by far the most liquid, widely-followed name in this regional-logistics group. Simply put: Japan's leading household-moving company, whose fortunes track how often people and businesses relocate.",
